{"tid":2272820,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工癲佬日常","createTime":"2020-11-05T09:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T10:34:20.000Z","uid":195944,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a9ae6eb53f85357ce896536a951328c320fb242","tid":2272820,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"返咗個幾禮拜工 發現好多同事都好壓抑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地公司同事就計佣嘅 接得多單就多啲bonus<br />\n<br />\n話說有個癲佬同事次次接電話都好細聲 個樣就七情上面 講講下整埋隻蘭花手出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我問佢點解咁做 佢話佢扮女人聲嘅話啲客會梳爽啲 咁bonus就多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問返其他人 佢bonus根本就無特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好撚癲 返工返到要扮女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a156113009038f36049454556be1e54ee1c1a0","tid":2272820,"uid":195944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"仲有啲次次講完電話 收晒線就講句 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cd3a03538bf589af7c37b48e38a4d439572bc0","tid":2272820,"uid":255880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51062fb26bb6bbe9376ced235cd622ab86a0b1a4","tid":2272820,"uid":205602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"都幾癲下"},{"pid":"82c69e5fe18421d35db3a8c9bcc4bd024fd1c289","tid":2272820,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42cd3a03538bf589af7c37b48e38a4d439572bc0","tid":2272820,"uid":255880,"like":1